
# Choosing a technology to create diagrams

## Context and Problem Statement

There are many diagrams that need to be created, like the C4 model, and the most suitable technology needs to be used for this

<!-- This is an optional element. Feel free to remove. -->
## Decision Drivers

* Creating diagrams

## Considered Options

* Draw.IO
* Word
* UML

## Decision Outcome

Chosen option: UML, it meeds the necessary criteria the best and allows for detailed diagrams


<!-- This is an optional element. Feel free to remove. -->
## Pros and Cons of the Options

### Draw.IO

* Good, because has a variety of preset shapes for UML
* Good, because widely used
* Bad, because have to arrange the diagram yourself, can get messy
* â€¦ <!-- numbers of pros and cons can vary -->

### Word

* Good, because widely used and accepted
* Bad, because no preset UML shapes
* Bad, because not enough space for diagram on a page

### UML

* Good, because widely used and accepted
* Good, because you can type the code in and it arranges it all for you
* Good, because UML is very easy to learn
* Good, because there is website dedicated to it, with documentation on its use. PlantUML
* Bad, because sometimes the arranging of the diagram can be awkward

